ygData.messageBody:
Hey All!

2 more people on Rodcet Mystic Alliance, we are growing fast! Bring your
characters on over! :)

Also, could all of the guildleaders on the other servers please e-mail me at
josephn@..., i'd like to set up an e-mail list for us to share ideas and
stuff.


-joe
